: dice          doc:"dice  ( n s -- sum )  Roll n s-sided dice

EXAMPLE:
3 6 dice  =>  number in range [3,18]"
  | in:n in:s out:sum |

  0 !sum
  @n 0 do
    @s randint !+sum
  loop
;
